<P>
   TV-GOLF-MEDIA (Akron, Ohio) _ The only thing more challenging
than driving a golf ball 300 yards down the center of the fairway
may be keeping the ball's flight centered and focused on a
television screen. Here's a behind-the-greens look at the
technologies that help network television cover golf tournaments.
By Seth Schiesel.
