   SOFTWARE-CODE-ASSESS (San Francisco) _ Analysis: When an
international team of researchers demonstrated recently that they
could break the standard lock that protects financial transactions
over the Internet, they sent a clear message to the e-commerce
community: Now is the time to get stronger locks. By Sara Robinson.
</P>
<P>
   (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Graphic is
being sent to NYT graphics clients.)
