<HEADLINE>
ONE ANGRY MAN: WHAT'S THE VERDICT WHEN THE MAYOR IS ALSO JURY
FOREMAN? 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By DAVID ROHDE   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
