   FBN-FALCONS _ ATLANTA _ As they head toward the 1999 season, the
Falcons face one key question that could fast send the team back to
its losing ways: Do the Falcons have enough speed at wide receiver
to spread the defense so Chris Chandler can operate and Jamal
Anderson run? The jury is out. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
